{"id": 440722, "slug": "pong-radial", "name": "Pong Radial", "name_original": "Pong Radial", "description": "<p>Use mouse or touch controls to move paddle around in order to keep ball in reach. You can also compete for higher score.</p>\n<p>This game was made for #TweetTweetJam which means, the sourcecode fits inside of 2 tweets (560 chars).I tried to do it with plain javascript .You can see it here (559 chars) :</p>\n<p><canvas height=\"300\" id=\"a\"><script>c=a.getContext`2d`;x=y=s=150;d=100;j=-1;n=p=0;t=e=>{c.fillStyle=e};r=e=>{c.translate(e,e)};setInterval(e=>{t`black`;c.fillRect(0,0,2*s,2*s);t`white`;j>0&&c.fillText('score:'+j,2,9);r(s);c.rotate(p);c.fillRect(d,-25,9,50);c.rotate(-p);r(-s);c.beginPath();c.arc(x,y,5,0,0.1,1);c.fill();o=Math.atan2(y-s,x-s)-p;h=Math.sqrt((x-s)*(x-s)+(y-s)*(y-s));w=h*Math.sin(o);i=d-h*Math.cos(o);if(w>-25&&w<25&&i<6&&i>=5){n=3.2+p;j++}x+=Math.cos(n);y+=Math.sin(n)},5);ontouchmove=onmousemove=e=>{p=Math.atan2(e.clientY-s,e.clientX-s)}</script><br/></canvas></p>", "metacritic": null, "released": "2020-05-06", "tba": false, "updated": "2020-05-08T05:06:06", "background_image": "https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/f67/f670720f3170a1eb6cdc8e2ba2951367.jpg", "website": "", "rating": 0.0, "rating_top": 0, "added_by_status": null, "playtime": 0, "achievements_count": 0, "ratings_count": 0, "suggestions_count": 3, "game_series_count": 0, "reviews_count": 0, "platforms": ["Web"], "developers": ["TGY"], "genres": [], "publishers": [], "esrb_rating": null}